An Interactive Map

Dewald Olivier

02 March 2019

Below is a map that shows the density of Airbnb listings in Cape Town, South Africa. One of the most attractive tourism city in the country.

Airbnb is a really popular option for people travelling to the city. I have created a map that shows all the listing available in and around the city.

## Assuming "longitude" and "latitude" are longitude and latitude, respectively
